title: Collet (Robert)
body: Ichthyologist and former director of the Zoological Museum of Christiania. Works: On a new Pediculate Fish from the Sea of Madeira (Proc Zool. Soc., X 1886); and Sur quelques poissons rapportés de Madère par le Prince de Monaco (Bullet. Soc. Zool. France XV 1890).

1886: Year of publication of 'On a new Pediculate Fish from the Sea of Madeira'
1890: Year of publication of 'Sur quelques poissons rapportés de Madère par le Prince de Monaco'
